   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Horos to the topogrammateis and village scribes, greeting. As soon as you read this order, join those who have been directed (to take part) in the voyage downstream according to what Eirenaios the (king's) cousin and dioiketes has written. We have sent for this purpose the people showing the letter. Give heed (?) to the letter (?) and act accordingly. The 4th year, Phaoph&lt;i&gt; 19.</ab>
         </div>
